text: The 2019 UConn Huskies men's soccer team represented the University of Connecticut during the 2019 NCAA Division I men's soccer season and the 2019 American Athletic Conference men's soccer season. The regular season began on August 30 and concluded on November 5. It was the program's 89th season fielding a men's varsity soccer team, and their 7th and final season in the AAC.
